  "title": "Sales & Marketing (Entry-Level)",
  "description": "<p>This entry-level role offers exposure to live events, client campaigns, and team-based marketing execution.</p><p>You’ll gain practical skills, performance-based rewards, and clear development pathways in a fast-paced environment.</p><p><strong>Ideal for:</strong> Individuals starting their career and eager to grow through experience.<br /><br /><strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p><p><ul><li>🌱 Entry-level candidates welcome</li><li>🎯 Motivated and coachable</li><li>👥 Team player with good attitude</li></ul></p><p><strong>What You’ll Be Doing</strong></p><p><ul><li>🎪 Assist in face-to-face marketing campaigns</li><li>🗣 Communicate brand value to customers</li><li>📈 Learn and grow through hands-on experience</li></ul></p><p><strong>What You’ll Gain</strong></p><p><ul><li>🚀 Career-building experience</li><li>📈 Growth and advancement opportunities</li><li>🤝 Supportive training environment</li><li>✈️ Travelling Opportunities</li></ul></p>",
